ActTerritorial Lands Act
PrecisORDER RESPECTING THE WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (TR'O-JU-WECH'IN HERITAGE SITE, TR'ONDËK HWËCH'IN FIRST NATION, Y.T.) - which provides for (a) the withdrawal from disposal of land in the Yukon until October 1, 2008, in order to facilitate the settlement of native land claims, and (b) the repeal of a similar Withdrawal from Disposal Order made on October 1, 1998.
RegistrationRegistration: SI/ 2003-0023 Publication Date: 2003-02-12
